text:
Multigenerational church community with Chinese, English, Kids and Youth services!
Chinese service- 845am
English service & Kids- 11am
Youth service - 1.30pm (except 1st Sunday of the month)

Vibrant and beautiful community ❤️
Take lobby 1’s lift to the second floor to access the space.
Bro Mark chua is a rising star in Church of Singapore, was inspired by his preaching today! It is a church that raise up the new generation of Christians! It an amazing church!
Super lovely community and hospitable brothers and sisters. Come meet God and a God centred community.
Pastor Mark's sermon was very heartfelt and I feel the Spirit leading this church.
this church is so nice and super good friendly church make me feel like home..
